Realm (YC S11) — San Francisco, Copenhagen, REMOTE<p>Realm is hiring Android Developers, iOS Developers, C++ developers, .NET developers, JavaScript developers, Designers, QA Engineers and more. See all positions at <a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io&#x2F;jobs" rel="nofollow">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io&#x2F;jobs</a><p>Realm (<a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io" rel="nofollow">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io</a>) is building a mobile database: a replacement for SQLIte &amp; Core Data. In 9 months, we became the 2nd-most deployed database in the world, running on well over 100M devices. Our headquarters are in San Francisco, but we also have a big office in Copenhagen, Denmark, and employees distributed around the world. We just announced we raised a $20M Series B last week [1][2][3][4]<p>See positions, locations and how to apply here: <a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io&#x2F;jobs" rel="nofollow">http:&#x2F;&#x2F;realm.io&#x2F;jobs</a><p>(If you have any questions, I’m VP Product at Realm and always happy to chat: tim@realm.io.)<p><pre><code>    [1]: http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.businessinsider.com&#x2F;realm-started-by-former-nokia-engineers-is-going-bonkers-2015-3
    [2]: http:&#x2F;&#x2F;techcrunch.com&#x2F;2015&#x2F;03&#x2F;24&#x2F;realm-can-expand-its-reach-with-20m-investment&#x2F;
    [3]: http:&#x2F;&#x2F;venturebeat.com&#x2F;2015&#x2F;03&#x2F;24&#x2F;mobile-database-startup-realm-picks-up-20m&#x2F;
    [4]: http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.forbes.com&#x2F;sites&#x2F;benkepes&#x2F;2015&#x2F;03&#x2F;24&#x2F;realm-picks-up-20m-to-further-its-mobile-ambitions&#x2F;</code></pre>
